com.interpss.core.aclf.contingency
Interface Contingency

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IEquivOutageBranch, IOutageIslanding, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
ContingencyImpl
public interface Contingency
extends NameTag, IEquivOutageBranch, IOutageIslanding

A representation of the model object 'Contingency'. A class for modeling a contingency

The following features are supported:

  • Total Islands
  • Outage Branches
  • Monitoring Branches
  • Island Buses
  • Equiv Outage Branches

See Also:
ContingencyPackage.getContingency()
